        <article eId="sec_2" class="prov1">
          <heading>Refusal of permit</heading>
          <num>2.</num>
          <paragraph class="prov2">
            <num>(1)</num>
            <content>
              <p>If the Secretary of State decides not to grant a permit, the Secretary of State must notify the operator who applied for it, within the period of 28 days beginning with the day after the day the decision is made, of the reasons for the decision.</p>
